subSubSection.paragraph:
Habitus (Fig. 
10
). Body oblong, slender, moderately convex dorsally and feebly convex ventrally, dull. Colour mostly blackish; mouthparts, gula, basal four antennomeres and tarsi dark brownish. Body mostly covered with short, thick, yellowish setae; gula mostly glabrous; antennae, apices of tibiae and tarsi covered with longer and thinner setae; labrum with longer and stronger setae at outer margin.
